data.description: Bring Reasonable Offer! You Must See This Inviting Townhome.  It's Perfect!  All On One Level Living! When You First Enter, You Will Undoubtedly feel The Openness of This Home With Its High Pitched Vaulted Ceilings And Smooth Flow Throughout! Enjoy The Beautiful Hardwood Floors Everywhere But In Kitchen and Baths! Custom Tiled Custom Backsplash and Granite Countertops! Kitchen has Handy Pantry and Next to that the Laundry Room! In The Living Room, the Owner Upgraded the Fireplace by Adding Stacked Stone for a More Custom Look!  This Serene Room Leads to a Special Private Deck Where You Can Sit For Hours If You Wish to Enjoy the Sublime Privacy!  Off The Living Room/Great Room is The Primary Suite with a Double Trey Ceiling!  This Room is Large and has an Ensuite With Double Vanity and an Upgraded Closet System.  Separate From the Master is a Large Secondary Bedroom Also With an Ensuite!  Wait....I'm Not Done Yet...There is a Wonderful Sun Porch for you to make an Office; a TV Room; Extra Sleepover Room, etc.  The Large Garage has a Large Storage Closet For Workshop, etc. Did I Mention a Basement....Unheard of In An Over 55 Community!  Don't Rent A Storage Unit When You Can Have All Your Belongings At Your Fingertips!  If You Require An In-Law Suite, You Have The Space To Finish!  Believe Me When I say, Life Is Good At 2417 Tree Arbor Way!  Come Check Us Out and I Think You Will Agree! We Are Ready to Sell!
